@1 = ~If ye think a river will keep me blade out of yer backs, think again.~
@2 = ~And nature bows to me!~
@3 = ~Try to run and ye'll feel my blade in yer back!~
@4 = ~Don't be a fool, let's get out of 'ere <CHARNAME>.~
@5 = ~Bring it on! I'll slaughter all of'em with ease.~
@6 = ~This be the place to prove yerselves!~
@7 = ~Killing demons be almost childplay. And they don't even cry when ye cut'em.~